{"tid":564382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司: CCTVB新聞報道並不正確 澄清未就UGL案作決定","createTime":"2018-02-18T02:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T06:10:47.000Z","uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd787797d3887f4ffe821dcaf06b9fe814d1564","tid":564382,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180218/57846395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57846395&d=2Zlj0CZ0yV0b4HDUAE93Rk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=180a2f3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57846395&h=adbfab49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180218/57846395</a><br />\n<br />\n前特首梁振英上任特首前簽協議，收取澳洲UGL公司5,000萬元，昨晚無綫新聞引述消息指，律政司已決定不就其收受UGL款項採取法律檢控行動，同時廉署亦結束調查。政務司司長張建宗今早出席電台訪問後就事件回應指，昨晚無綫新聞所披露純粹揣測，律政司適時會作出交代，現階段不宜作評論。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英2011年參選特首，2014年有澳洲傳媒披露，他上任前以戴德梁行董事身份與澳洲企業UGL簽訂秘密協議，以換取約5,000萬港元報酬，部分款項在上任後收取，但未有申報，其後有政黨向廉署舉報。律政司回覆《蘋果》查詢時澄清，有關UGL案件律政司已決定不作檢控的報道，並不正確，律政司並未就該案件是否提出檢控作出決定。發言人重申，由於案件尚未完結，不會就案件透露任何內容。"},{"pid":"0dd4054e129416e461e793d9d9ce802afd83daed","tid":564382,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075389c17e6aa7ad3a79bb80d1dd7e482d093c93","tid":564382,"uid":162424,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:29:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f46979514a5158d28ff4329e72b6f983439c6808","tid":564382,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"係咪呀，CCTVB 海外版講係決定咗，家中老父重話今次泛民冇得出聲，律政司係請咗英國律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b930c522f1f32bd3d40be8b42687c07b50934